  "body": "#### Expected behaviour\r\n\r\nFor turbo geth to not place things at the top level in my home directory (even if they are *hidden* files :smile: ) but instead to use the [XDG standard](https://specifications.freedesktop.org/basedir-spec/basedir-spec-latest.html) and to place things somewhere like `$XDG_DATA_HOME/turbogeth`\r\n\r\n#### Actual behaviour\r\n\r\nThe client creates a hidden directory under `$HOME/.turbogeth` where it stores things\r\n\r\n#### Steps to reproduce the behaviour\r\n\r\nRun the client",
