    "body": "The spec defines defaults for when these variables are not set:\r\n\r\n>  $XDG_DATA_HOME defines the base directory relative to which user specific data files should be stored. If $XDG_DATA_HOME is either not set or empty, a default equal to $HOME/.local/share should be used. \r\n\r\nYou can see our simple python module that we use for these directories which also shows the defaults: https://github.com/ethereum/trinity/blob/master/trinity/_utils/xdg.py",
